{"tid":697080,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"文青系校花曝光　竟神似結衣 🙄","createTime":"2018-06-10T16:05:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T05:27:22.000Z","uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"09301e347c14f874aa87a9261ca4b08ab6f36421","tid":697080,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:05:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YyQPaNQrs0w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYyQPaNQrs0w&d=9ZkRbwUhydai648jsR7k%2BNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=7f7ea4ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YyQPaNQrs0w</a><br />\n成大新垣結衣桃花眼<br />\n<br />\n點睇？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15d6cc67e3989af262219fc6d7c8e48f9f870d9f","tid":697080,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:05:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CPMemftWv1k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCPMemftWv1k&d=9ZkRbwUhydai648jsR7k%2BNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=70487f10\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CPMemftWv1k</a><br />\n酷似新垣結衣 文化腰窩妹 3%美蹟現身"},{"pid":"1a0d0fa4f262b242944041bea3301a96e60051ce","tid":697080,"uid":5921,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:06:23.000Z","msg":"驗眼.jpg"},{"pid":"6c5e6ad400bcaa73724b88b14409fda9562c8e84","tid":697080,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:06:26.000Z","msg":"藝人楊子儀日前到台南成功大學，尋找神似日本女星新垣結衣的「文青系校花」羅珮恩。目前就讀成功大學台灣文學系三年級的羅珮恩，剛入學時，曾在學校FB板上發問，沒想到被眾多學長肉搜，造成全校轟動，只因照片太吸睛，甚至有位學長在大學迎新時當著3000多人面前，當眾求認識。"},{"pid":"4808edf6a8bcecbcfa1f21aaf4f8668a5dd593fe","tid":697080,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:07:04.000Z","msg":"個個都話自己似明星 咪撚玩啦"},{"pid":"f0dee9efa0dbbc61edeccd2e79d6b92a5b80892e","tid":697080,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:07:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/storage.googleapis.com/nownews2017/nownews_production/images/5b1bd981b1f76e244f114ff5_201806092143.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Fnownews2017%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F5b1bd981b1f76e244f114ff5_201806092143.jpg&h=88a92c4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a13b384de3464ff35606b1a5c3794d3f539f089","tid":697080,"uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:07:20.000Z","msg":"屌那星是撚但有條女對眼大啲都話似結衣<br />\n全部仆街死啦"},{"pid":"f36eaa16d37f14feb154e68b532823ad48c542ad","tid":697080,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:07:42.000Z","msg":"平時熱愛台灣文學詩集的珮恩，文青感十足，私底下還是個會自彈自唱的才女，手指上都是練習吉他的繭，讓楊子儀直呼，「真的是練家子。」但同學爆料，指出羅珮恩其實是超級睡神，曾睡超過24小時，打了幾百通電話也叫不醒，楊子儀還想了一個狀況劇給她，讓她假裝自己今天睡過頭，沒想到她用又呆萌又楚楚可憐的眼神望著他說：「對不起。」直接讓楊子儀一秒融化。"},{"pid":"529d5b30544471b2c815d492bb7182a2f8be6332","tid":697080,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:08:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/storage.googleapis.com/nownews2017/nownews_production/images/5b1bd9070ce59b241e9bcf39_201806092141.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Fnownews2017%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F5b1bd9070ce59b241e9bcf39_201806092141.jpg&h=36ffd1bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲羅珮恩神似新垣結衣。（圖／校盟影業提供 , 2018.6.9）"},{"pid":"f2ba42a6473cdc58f05f945d2bb48952f4383e72","tid":697080,"uid":50595,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:08:48.000Z","msg":"好撚造作好嘔心啊"},{"pid":"010bb0dedf5fdc99d65ad25f89c01d3e13951423","tid":697080,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:09:36.000Z","msg":"長相甜美可愛的羅佩恩，在節目中爆料，不敢在外面廁所上大號，無論如何一定要回家才行，楊子儀感同身受，因為他也是這樣的人，還反問校花：「妳上大號的時候是不是要脫光光？」她害羞回答，「是。」"},{"pid":"f8f9dc0c575ba586839ddefd642bc0dbdb67222b","tid":697080,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/storage.googleapis.com/nownews2017/nownews_production/images/5b1bd95c0ce59b241e9bcf3a_201806092142.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Fnownews2017%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F5b1bd95c0ce59b241e9bcf3a_201806092142.jpg&h=ab50fe2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲羅珮恩神似新垣結衣。（圖／校盟影業提供 , 2018.6.9）"},{"pid":"65be99c96dfd98e856a55bf6184869ca9bbcf15e","tid":697080,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:14:01.000Z","msg":"好有p圖feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f0c8443434e380cd0f6c318b98e5ace56fccc4d","tid":697080,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:14:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/christinexlo/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fchristinexlo%2F&d=9ZkRbwUhydai648jsR7k%2BNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=7712631c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/christinexlo/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ebf224b902e64486678fb2bb8e67ee9edf3c4af1","tid":697080,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4f0c8443434e380cd0f6c318b98e5ace56fccc4d","tid":697080,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:14:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/christinexlo/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fchristinexlo%2F&d=9ZkRbwUhydai648js